{"tid":1894452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[Youtube屌你老母］徐加睛新歌《十四天》講肺炎被隔離既心情 都中黃標","createTime":"2020-02-24T02:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T05:54:17.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"931d5e1d2cfce413b06bee41b73b9bf492adf457","tid":1894452,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:33:23.000Z","msg":"到底「武漢肺炎」嘅威力有幾大？原來單係喺hashtag打呢四個字，已經足以令到YouTube面色大變。<br />\n<br />\n話說歌手Rona徐加睛近日推出咗一首自己有份作曲嘅新歌《十四天》。顧名思義，呢首歌嘅創作靈感，係源自武漢病毒性肺炎嘅疫情。但當佢將呢首歌嘅MV，分別upload上Facebook同YouTube之後，佢就發覺MV喺YouTube嘅click rate，竟然出奇地遠低於Facebook。初頭佢都不以為意，直到今日中午，當佢再click入YouTube條link嗰陣，先至發覺條片原來已經被「黃標」，即係被評為「不適合多數廣告客戶」。<br />\n<br />\nRona質疑，「武漢肺炎」本身係一場全民都要共同面對嘅疫症，唔應該被視為一個敏感政治議題。佢強調，呢首歌係因應香港人面對疫情嘅實際境況而誕生。對象除咗包括一眾飽受壓力嘅前線醫護人員之外，亦希望可以為香港人帶嚟點滴嘅鼓勵。由始至終，佢並無將內地人，列為呢首歌嘅目標受眾。如果單純因為hashtag有呢四個大字，YouTube就要加以封殺嘅話，佢會感到相當無奈。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣聽呢首歌嘅朋友，可以click入下面條link：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/996322427118132/posts/2778181745598849/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F996322427118132%2Fposts%2F2778181745598849%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=5495be74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/996322427118132/posts/2778181745598849/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3NWMBTXWMXw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3NWMBTXWMXw&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=57ae20bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3NWMBTXWMXw</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/seelifehk/?refid=52&amp;__tn__=C-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fseelifehk%2F%3Frefid%3D52%26__tn__%3DC-R&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=a18f9060\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/seelifehk/?refid=52&amp;__tn__=C-R</a><br />\n<br />\nBtw好聽過牛華學友9條街"},{"pid":"ec429dafe66b6f827ceec5dbf8991f80d68426f7","tid":1894452,"uid":73248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:48:38.000Z","msg":"黃標左係米無得洗白番?"},{"pid":"23d3023b1fe5d8446c273ebbd9f77fc4d9be4a94","tid":1894452,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec429dafe66b6f827ceec5dbf8991f80d68426f7","tid":1894452,"uid":73248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:48:38.000Z","msg":"黃標左係米無得洗白番?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:54:52.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n但通常一出片最多views<br />\n後尾解番都蝕大部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f7629ff813c92a7f029ab5bc7a0db37a2a8b62","tid":1894452,"uid":5103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T03:32:44.000Z","msg":"我地小隊依家正努力整合緊屬於我地香港本土YouTube channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打們可以支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n攻擊重要,防守都好重要<br />\n如果出面做攻擊,我地會做好防守依一個環節<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地都仲有一班本土channel須要我地大力支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">目標對每個本土channel：subscibe+㩒鐘仔+share俾10個fd+睇片+留言+like </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">覺唔覺得香港真係無乜本土YouTube Channel? (2.1)</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1886497\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1886497</a>"},{"pid":"a39bb761d21c7262fe4dd1e79453bb68e667e5a5","tid":1894452,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:58:29.000Z","msg":"同